{"tid":2157811,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"半澤直樹2》落戶香港　有得睇正版","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:49:16.000Z","uid":150610,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16d8af071a67cee4d39089efa8b6652bb77d1f68","tid":2157811,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"日劇《半澤直樹2》在日本收視率遙遙領先，播放第三集的收視率達23.2，比首兩集的22及22.1更高，各地電視台正爭奪《半澤直樹2》播映權，香港亦將有得播放，由電視廣播（00511，TVB）的mytvsuper的日劇頻道播放。<br />\n<br />\n《半澤直樹2》為王牌電視劇，本地各電視台及<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">netflix</span></span>等，均搶奪日劇、韓劇，甚至大熱的卡通動畫，以開拓不同喜好的客戶，《半澤直樹2》花落誰家，亦為本地視頻大戰的一個重頭戲。<br />\n<br />\n《半澤直樹2》的原著為池井戶潤，預期劇集會改篇《失落世代的逆襲》、《銀翼的伊卡洛斯》等小說的內容。<br />\n<br />\n池井戶潤善寫商戰類型小說，除了《半澤直樹》系列，《下町火箭》、《花咲舞不會沉默》、《民王》、《羅斯福遊戲》、《彬與瑛》等，均有改篇電視劇，均是收視王牌。<br />\n<br />\n記者：譚志偉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDKLM，搞到我SUB咗NETFLIX，點知根本冇，FUCKING FAKE NEWS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7848b5e6ea5db8ec3b5af3b4f97c48d158973fad","tid":2157811,"uid":150610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"係我戇鳩，信埋啲碌撚藍報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0694791c4b5c22d9d92deddc987434ecd3393d37","tid":2157811,"uid":320487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"搶奪咋 <br />\n都冇話搶到"},{"pid":"7ee06b82d54fbf2ed897f3fd1e42774d5aae7b6d","tid":2157811,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset